{
    "title": "Vale Quanto Pesa",
    "artist": "Luiz Melodia",
    "composer": "Luíz Melodia",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quanto você ganha pra me enganar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quanto você paga pra me ver sofrer</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(9)\">D7(9)</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E quanto você força pra me derreter</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sou forte feito cobra coral</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Semente brota em qualquer local</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D4\">D4</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um velho novo cartão postal, cartão postal</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Aquela madrugada deu em nada, deu em muito, deu em sol</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>                                                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Aquele seu desejo me deu medo, me deu força, me deu mal</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ai de mim, de nós dois</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ai de mim, de nós dois</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vale quanto pesa, reza a lesa de nós dois</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ai de mim, de nós dois</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Temos um passado já marcado não podemos mentir</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Beijos demorados afirmados não podemos mentir</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ai de mim, de nós dois</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ai de mim, de nós dois</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vale quanto pesa, reza a lesa de nós dois</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ai de mim, de nós dois</span>\n",
